        <otherDetails xml:lang="en">Validation warnings:

- Mass and/or economic deficit in activity dataset exceeds either 0.1% of input or output sum:

Property 'dry mass':
 - Input='0', Output='1'
 - Input &lt; output by 1 kg (100% of output)

Property 'wet mass':
 - Input='0', Output='1'
